        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This sharp-taloned <em>+1 striking spiked gauntlet</em> appears to have been crafted from dragon scales, with claws built from iron. In addition to the typical weapon traits, a Cinderclaw gauntlet has the versatile S trait.</p>\n<p>On a critical hit, the <em>Cinderclaw gauntlet</em> deals an additional 1d6 fire damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">R</span> command</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your attack roll with the <em>Cinderclaw gauntlet</em> is a critical success.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The creature you hit must succeed at a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:19|showDC:owner] save or be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} by the gauntlet's acrid smoke. Creatures that don't need to breathe are immune.</p>"
